"607","<TYPE>EX-99.77M MERGERS"
"608","<SEQUENCE>3"
"609","<FILENAME>merger-V106.txt"
"610","<DESCRIPTION>MERGER LETTER"
"611","<TEXT>"
"612","ITEM 77M: Mergers"
"613","Value Line Income & Growth Fund, Inc. - Value Line Convertible"
"614","Fund, Inc."
"615","On December 15, 2011, a special Meeting of Shareholders"
"616","(the Meeting) of the Value Line Convertible Fund, Inc."
"617","(the Acquired Fund) was held to consider and vote upon a Plan of"
"618","Reorganization (the Reorganization) between the Value Line"
"619","Convertible Fund, Inc. and Value Line Income & Growth Fund, Inc."
"620","(the Surviving Fund)."
"621","On December 16, 2011, the Surviving Fund acquired all of the assets"
